ariba.ui.wizard.meta
Class WizardMeta

java.lang.Object
  ariba.ui.wizard.meta.GenericMeta
      ariba.ui.wizard.meta.WizardMeta

public final class WizardMeta
extends GenericMeta

WizardMeta is the runtime counterpart to an XML definition of a wizard. It represents all the static information about a particular wizard flow, i.e. the name of the wizard, the steps and frames used in the process, custom actions, etc.
